net.sf.antcontrib.logic

Class OutOfDate

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.tools.ant.ProjectComponent
      • org.apache.tools.ant.Task
        • net.sf.antcontrib.logic.OutOfDate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, org.apache.tools.ant.taskdefs.condition.Condition

    public class OutOfDate
extends org.apache.tools.ant.Task
implements org.apache.tools.ant.taskdefs.condition.Condition
    Task to help in calling tasks if generated files are older than source files. Sets a given property or runs an internal task.

    Based on UpToDate task

    Author:
    Peter Reilly
